      Replaces a series of methods from the specified class For example, modifying the method to acept a more generic type (Dog -> Animal): // Creating MethodType MethodType newType = MethodType.methodType(void.class, Pet.class); // Modifying the method Intercessor.replaceMethod(Owner.class, new jmplib.reflect.Method("addPet", newType, "this.pet = dog;"));
